_sText:
Includes

kz_aggressive
kz_asendrix
kz_bhop_cage
kz_hb_holy
kzro_raincliff

Extra
bhop_asendrix_v1
kz_aggressive_ez

Descriptions

kz_aggressive
Original map by Timmycakes, KZMOD remake by Hardcore
contains 3 courses: kz_aggressive, kz_cave and bkz_polar_climber

kz_asendrix
Original map by Hardcore and Xinc
contains 3 courses: kz_asendrix, bhop_asendrix and kz_bhop_asendrix
notes for server owners: set shavit_misc_startonspawn 0 and start zone should be placed as shown in the gamebanana photo.

kz_bhop_cage
Original map author unknown
contains 1 course: kz_bhop_cage

kz_hb_holy
Original map by pacMan
contains 3 courses: kz_hb_holy (which is the kz + bhop course combined + extra), kz course and bhop course.
notes: the main course starts on the purple in the climb section and finishes in the purple on the bhop section.

kzro_raincliff
Original map by fuZzy1, KZMOD port by pacMan
contains 1 course: kz_raincliff
notes: intended to played with a velocity limit either 400 velocity or strafe settings (sv_enablebunnyhopping 0), NL styles can skip most of the map.

kz_aggressive_ez
The easy course from kz_aggressive, bonuses are identical.

bhop_asendrix_v1
Just the bhop + lj course from kz_asendrix with the kz section removed
